  <brief_title>A Study of the Treatment of Type 2 Diabetes With an Insulin Infusion Pump</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Stepwise Basal Insulin Dose Titration Study Using Continuous Subcutaneous Insulin Infusion (CSII) in Oral Antidiabetic Drug-Treated Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Subjects Followed by a 10-Week Out-Patient Maintenance Phase</official_title>
