  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America (USA). This is an in-patient trial
      investigating stepwise dose increase in a period of up to 3-weeks followed by a 10-week
      out-patient maintenance period. A telephone contact visit is scheduled as a follow-up for the
      final clinic visit. A subject's participation in this trial would be expected to be up to 16
      weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
