  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes diagnosis at least 2 years ago

          -  Body Mass Index (BMI): 26-40 kg/m^2 (both inclusive)

          -  HbA1c: 7.5-10% (both inclusive)

          -  FPG values at least 140 mg/dl (7.8 mmol/l)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of drugs, which may interfere with the interpretation of trial results or are
             known to cause clinically relevant interference with insulin action or glucose
             utilization (steroids or non-specific beta-blockers)

          -  Current addiction to alcohol or substances of abuse or positive results on urine
             screen for drug and alcohol use

          -  Known or suspected allergy to trial products or related products
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
